{"tid":1938591,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"好想養狗狗","createTime":"2020-03-22T15:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T08:25:50.000Z","uid":325750,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bea40185619c29b3ad2b26ddf781d396c7371783","tid":1938591,"uid":325750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:49:45.000Z","msg":"由細到大都好鐘意狗狗 <br />\n有做過狗義工 平時又會借啲意去狗公園摸下啲狗狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係好想自己養一隻<br />\n自己仲讀緊大學 幾年後先畢業 <br />\n雖然有幾萬儲蓄 但係每個月嘅parttime錢都唔係話多 係唔係應該等到出嚟做野先好養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然屋企人有咩事會幫我比住先 但係見有po話睇醫生睇左成八萬 我又打消左養狗嘅念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e89e5e0fc54ebf25b36ba1e79e76edd0b2056a3","tid":1938591,"uid":73959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:50:41.000Z","msg":"領養thx"},{"pid":"02ecb28cb25b9090334c15b13561eca6c1ecff4a","tid":1938591,"uid":167567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都想.... 狗狗好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415b09eadbd22ab077c289ef77d5f8526b43a82d","tid":1938591,"uid":27807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:51:15.000Z","msg":"有能力先好搞，同埋最好去領養"},{"pid":"0765e99c1db7411f4185c76bb7d109b4c1494f19","tid":1938591,"uid":325750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e89e5e0fc54ebf25b36ba1e79e76edd0b2056a3","tid":1938591,"uid":73959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:50:41.000Z","msg":"領養thx"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T15:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日日po住啲領養page 但係都唔關我事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced248d11a47a6519abe4100091753fe6fefc943","tid":1