al/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係好想自己養一隻<br />\n自己仲讀緊大學 幾年後先畢業 <br />\n雖然有幾萬儲蓄 但係每個月嘅parttime錢都唔係話多 係唔係應該等到出嚟做野先好養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然屋企人有咩事會幫我比住先 但係見有po話睇醫生睇左成八萬 我又打消左養狗嘅念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T06:40:02.000Z","msg":"申請做PT陪狗員?<br />\n雖然唔知衣家仲有冇人幫襯"},{"pid":"4570ab12c2d531c2617568af765b1f88bedcc6d0","tid":1938591,"uid":309268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T17:30:44.000Z","msg":"有興趣領養成犬唐狗嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1642330147/posts/10219176493836831/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1642330147%2Fposts%2F10219176493836831%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdM0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=920684cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1642330147/posts/10219176493836831/?d=n</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/mongrelclub.hk/permalink/2926745080697165/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fmongrelclub.hk%2Fpermalink%2F2926745080697165%2F&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdM0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=71ae52dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/mongrelclub.hk/permalink/2926745080697165/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1153241522/posts/10222033856852818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1153241522%2Fposts%2F10222033856852818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdM0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=a3a2c942\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1153241522/posts/10222033856852818/?d=n</a><br />\n或領養年老嘅品種狗？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/999884203414931/permalink/3602269086509750/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F999884203414931%2Fpermalink%2F3602269086509750%2F&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdM0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5i